105
00:08:22.168 --> 00:08:23.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
YASU

106
00:08:24.170 --> 00:08:29.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
