107
00:08:29.091 --> 00:08:31.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Well, a better term would be</i>
<i>our queen bee.</i>

108
00:08:32.678 --> 00:08:37.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
