<i>smiling brightened the place up.</i>

109
00:08:37.308 --> 00:08:39.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It gave everyone added energy</i>
<i>in the studio</i>

110
00:08:39.227 --> 00:08:40.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
