124
00:09:19.225 --> 00:09:21.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You want one too, Misato?
-Yes!

125
00:09:21.561 --> 00:09:23.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
