147
00:10:50.316 --> 00:10:52.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Because you’ve always had the tendency

148
00:10:52.193 --> 00:10:54.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to take things
too negatively and seriously.

149
00:10:55.363 --> 00:10:58.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hachi seems to be really
affectionate with you,

150
00:10:58.199 --> 00:11:00.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so you should be glad that
someone cares about you so much.

151
00:11:01.243 --> 00:11:04.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Treat her as well as your heart desires.

152
00:11:04.455 --> 00:11:06.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There’s nothing wrong with that.

153
00:11:07.208 --> 00:11:08.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Yeah, but…</i>

154
00:11:08.793 --> 00:11:09.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Edamame!</i>

155
00:11:09.710 --> 00:11:12.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Well, now that you mention it,</i>
<i>that does make sense.</i>

156
00:11:13.130 --> 00:11:15.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But I hate feeling persuaded like that!</i>

157
00:11:15.424 --> 00:11:19.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Why am I always influenced</i>
<i>by what Ren says or does?</i>

158
00:11:20.179 --> 00:11:21.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I can understand that</i>
<i>being the case in the past,</i>

159
00:11:21.639 --> 00:11:23.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>but why is it still like that?</i>

160
00:11:23.432 --> 00:11:25.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I haven’t matured a bit.</i>

161
00:11:25.726 --> 00:11:28.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>First of all, I had no intention</i>
<i>of getting back together with him.</i>

162
00:11:28.938 --> 00:11:32.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>So why am I seeing him</i>
<i>like a part-time wife?</i>

163
00:11:33.025 --> 00:11:37.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why am I making miso soup?
