165
00:12:01.429 --> 00:12:04.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, where’s your on-off switch?

166
00:12:05.224 --> 00:12:07.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I don’t have one.</i>

167
00:12:12.314 --> 00:12:14.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>If there is one, install it in me.</i>

168
00:12:15.818 --> 00:12:19.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Someone… please adjust me.</i>

169
00:12:21.907 --> 00:12:26.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Why does my heart still burn</i>

170
00:12:27.913 --> 00:12:29.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>so hot?</i>

171
00:12:44.555 --> 00:12:45.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
