275
00:20:19.051 --> 00:20:22.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
It’s nothing compared to the future house
of Nana from BLAST.

276
00:20:22.512 --> 00:20:24.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
I’ll show you, Demon Lord!

277
00:20:24.848 --> 00:20:27.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
I see you’ve also become
a believer of the Demon Lord.

278
00:20:27.351 --> 00:20:31.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
